S.W.K., Individually and as Administratrix Ad Prosequendum of the Estate of J.B.K., Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
ATLANTIC HEALTH SYSTEM, INC., Morristown Medical Center, Emergency Medical Associates of New Jersey, PA, Steven P. Gohsler, M.D., and Alfredo Tapia, M.D., Defendants-Respondents. S.W.K., Individually and as Administratrix Ad Prosequendum of the Estate of J.B.K., Plaintiff,
v.
Morristown Medical Center, et al., Defendants. C-732 September Term 2018
082368 Supreme Court of New Jersey. March 21, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-00479045 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
